snippet.title: The Sims 3 70s, 80s, & 90s Stuff
snippet.description: Give your Sims the hottest looks and coolest décor from yesteryear with The Sims 3 70s, 80s, & 90s Stuff. Bring back all the crazy trends, from feathered hair to parachute pants to console stereos as your Sims warp back in time. Available January, 2013.
